Submit for the purposes of printing on the license and publication on the Health Professional Licensing Administration website, two (2) recent passport-type color photographs measuring two inches by two inches (2&#8242;x2&#8243;) which clearly
        expose the area from the top of the forehead to the bottom of the chin. Such photographs shall be submitted for the renewal period commencing six (6) years from the date of the initial application or initial registration and thereafter, every
        six (6) years at the date of each subsequent renewal;
